Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.54,0:21:49.13,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}是時候上陣了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.17,0:21:51.34,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不知何為失敗
